divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife and I were traveling North on Hwy 169 just North of Garrison, Mn. My wife was driving and she pointed out what appeared to be headlights of a plane and said something to the effect of ���look how low he is flying���. I looked to the Northwest of our line of travel and saw what appeared to be one plane following another very low over the trees. I said something to the effect of ���there are two of them, and look how close they are following each other. They must be military or maybe helicopters.���. The first object crossed Hwy 169 in front of us and disappeared. We passed right under the second object and I stuck my head out of the passenger window and initially was looking straight up at it. I could see it silhouetted against the stars. It was at this point that I realized that it wasn���t any normal plane, or helicopter. It looked similar to the outline of a stealth jet. The object went out over Lake Mille Lacs. It was moving too slow to be a plane and it wasn���t making any noise. It only had green lights on its underside and it wasn���t shaped like a plane
Summary: two flying objects crossed path. passed under second object. no sound and going to slow with improper lighting.
